From the chart of accounts, it is possible to use the 'Balance by movement type' action, which allows you to analyze the balance of opening/closing operations.

<img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000258-0/App SGL Slide 35_Andrea Giordani_cr_TOP.png"><br>

This page, therefore, allows you to analyze the totals by differentiating by "entry type".

<img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000258-0/App SGL Slide 35_Andrea Giordani_cr_BOTTOM.png"><br>

The movement type is the EOS option field that is automatically populated by the standard closing balance or  opening/closing income statement reports.